.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bluemaster, siglo, alhambra
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the owner of the frog and the cain-smoker##2
6. the alhambra-smoker is between the person watching western movies and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Cigar         | bluemaster    | alhambra | siglo | cain |

