.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: corn, nectarine, onion, plum
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, polish, american
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, rat, turtle
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the chinese is on the right of the american##1
 4. the person eating corn is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the canadian is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2
 9. the person eating plum is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the canadian is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | mirinda    | sprite      | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | corn        | plum       | onion       | nectarine     |
| Nationality      | polish | canadian | american | chinese        |
| Pet        | horse       | turtle     | rat         | dog           |

